quran[23]{c,v,t}:
  26,184,"Hulee On Tagu…óo on, O tagi kadi moftaaji adinoo…ói …óin huliron Mo fii wata O jippin e moo…óon Lepte Makko …óen."
  26,185,"Yim…ďe Su'aybu …ďen wi'ani Su'aybu: Pellet, an ko a jeyaa…óo …ďen …ďe mbilewu he…ďi …óum laawi …óuu…óu…ói haa mbilewu ngun fooli hakkille maa…óa …óen, ngu wirni …óe."
  26,186,"A wonaali si wanaa ko a …ďanndunke wano amen, alaa ko senndumaa e amen, ko honno wonirtaa Nulaa…óo? Men jikkaama si wanaa ko a fenoowo e kon ko nodditi…óaa …óum wonndema an ko a Nulaa…óo."
  26,187,"Awa li…ďu e hoore amen kunte immorde ka kammu si tawii a wonii goongu…óo e ko nodditi…óaa kon."
  26,188,"Su'aybu maakani …ďe: ko Joomi am woni Anndu…óo kon ko golloton immorde e sirku e geddi, hay e huunde e golle moo…óon …óen suu…óanaaki Mo."
  26,189,"∆Āe jokkindiri fennugol ngol, he…ďi …ďe Lepte maw…óe nokku ka …óowdini …ďe duulere …ďaawo √Īalaande sa…ótunde nguli, o saa∆īini e dow ma…ď…ďe yiite nge sunni …ďe. Pellet, √Īalnde halkeede ma…ď…ďe …óum wonuno √Īalaande mawnunde kulol."
  26,190,"Pellet, wonii e koo ko jaŇčtaa …óoo immorde e halkeede yim…ďe Su'aybu …ďen (yo o his) tasakuyee, wonannde taskotoo…ďe …ďen, …ďur…ďe heewude e ma…ď…ďe wonaali gom…óin…ďe."
  26,191,"Anndu Joomi maa…óa -an Nulaa…óo- ko Kanko woni teddu…óo Yo…ďtotoo…óo ay…ďe Makko …ďen, Yurmetee…óo on tuubu…óo immorde e jeyaa…ďe Makko …ďen."
  26,192,"E pellet, ndee Alqur'aanaare tellinaande e Muhammadu (yo Alla juulu e makko hisina) ko jippinaande immorde Jooma tageefooji …óin."
  26,193,"Jippinii nde Jibriila hoolaa…óo on (yo o his)."
  26,194,"O jippinii nde ka …ďernde maa…óa -an Nulaa…óo- fii yo a wonu jeyaa…óo e …ďen Nulaa…ďe jertinoo…ďe yim…ďe …ďen, …ďe hul…ďinira…ďe Lepte Alla …óen."
  26,195,"O jippininde e …óemngal Aarabu …ďanngungal."
  26,196,"Pellet, ndee Alqur'aanaare nde jaŇčtanooma ka defte adinoo…ďe …ďen, gom…óii Defte kammuyankooje adinoo…óe …óen wewliniriino nde."
  26,197,"Kaa hara wonanaali …ďee fennu…ďe ma maande e goongugol maa…óa, nde tawata anndu…ďe …ďen ka …ďi…ó…ďe Israa'iila no anndi goongugol ko jippinaa kon e maa…óa, wano Abdullaahi bun Salaami."
  26,198,"Sinndo Men jippinno ndee Alqur'aanaare e dow wo…ď…ďe e …ďen ajamiyankoo…ďe …ďe wowlataa …óemngal Aarabu ngal,"
  26,199,"O janngi nde e dow ma…ď…ďe, …ďe wonataa gom…óin…ďe nde; sabu arma …ďe wi'a: Men faamataa nde, koni yo …ďe yettu Alla …ďaa O jippinii [nde] ka haala ma…ď…ďe."
  26,200,"Ko wano nii, Men naadiri fennugol ngol e keefeeru ngun e nder …ďer…óe bon…ďe …ďen."
  26,201,"∆Āe waylataa ko …ďe woni kon e muu…óum immorde keefeeru ngun, …ďe gom…óintaa haa …ďe yi'a Lepte muusu…óe …óen."
  26,202,"∆äee Lepte ara e ma…ď…ďe e juhal, hara …ďe anndaa arugol majje haa …óe juha …ďe."
  26,203,"Hara hi…ďe wi'a tuma Lepte …óen jippotoo e ma…ď…ďe e juhal immorde e sa…ótugol nimse …óen: Taw si ko men nennantee…ďe haa men tuuba ka Alla?!"
  26,204,"Enee, hara ko Lepte Amen …óen …ďee heefer…ďe hawjanta hara hi…ďe wi'a: Men gom…óintaa ma haa li…ďaa kammu ngun e hoore amen kunte, wano aa∆īor…óaa non?!"
  26,205,"Humpitam -an Nulaa…óo- si Men dakmitii …ďee heefer…ďe …óuurnii…ďe e gom…óinngol ko addu…óaa kon, e neemaaji jamaanu juutungu."
  26,206,"Refti ari e ma…ď…ďe …ďaawo ngun jamaanu ngu …ďe he…ďi e muu…óum …óin neemaaji, ko …ďe wonanoo fodeede kon immorde e Lepte …óen."